
### Get Wallet Status
GET http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/status
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Transaction History
GET http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/transactions
Accept: application/json

###

### Reset Wallet (Default $100)
POST http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startingBalance": null
}

###

### Reset Wallet (Custom Amount)
POST http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startingBalance": 250.00
}

###

### Test Reserve Funds ($50)
POST http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/test-reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50.00
}

###

### Test Reserve Funds ($25)
POST http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/test-reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 25.00
}

###

### Test Release Funds (Replace with actual TicketId from reserve response)
POST http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/test-release
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 25.00,
  "ticketId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

