### Full Test Sequence
# 1. Get initial status
GET http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/status

###

# 2. Reset wallet to $200
POST http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startingBalance": 200.00
}

###

# 3. Reserve $75
POST http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/test-reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 75.00
}

###

# 4. Check status after reserve
GET http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/status

###

# 5. Check transaction history
GET http://localhost:5095/api/wallet/transactions

